File organization:

App-specific components in apps/{app}/src/components
Shared components in packages/ui/src
App-specific utilities in apps/{app}/src/utils
Shared utilities in packages/utils/src


Code style:

PascalCase for components
camelCase for utility functions
kebab-case for API routes

Imports order:

React/Next.js imports first
Third-party libraries next
Internal modules last
Styling imports at the end


Security focus:

Never expose service_role keys in client code
Use parameterized queries
Implement proper authentication checks
Follow Row Level Security best practices
